{"tid":104600,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想跑步減肚腩    但對腳唔生性?","createTime":"2017-02-02T08:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T14:13:49.000Z","uid":79141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1e5920601ca4e07c46954218005cfd89510756","tid":104600,"uid":79141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"講下基本資料先   <br />\n<br />\n27歲   165高   65kg  <br />\n手腳有肉但唔&quot;泡&quot;   主要有胃腩+肚腩<br />\n<br />\n而家做緊跑步帶氧燒脂  +   做機增肌  <br />\n跑步速度中上   但經常跑十分鐘已經想放棄    (身已暖但未出汗)   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呼吸還可以    但對腳愈黎愈重   均速再跑都難   減速跑會仲辛苦<br />\n加速....唔好玩啦   會仆街  <br />\n咁既情況係咪肌肉耐力唔夠?  <br />\n<br />\n求指點"},{"pid":"eb9e40fda0ed8ef3ed15e1dd86d74b75a85ac5da","tid":104600,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"a6f835fd99bda8ce7b94a5e9938c05a11f592af5","tid":104600,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"減肥黎講 跑得耐但慢好快過跑得短但快"},{"pid":"02a63fe3a5e3cc6d48c69d4000ddcf939430ff4f","tid":104600,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"踩健身單車"},{"pid":"1a82c403fd9884afd38184c33d731aaafa214de2","tid":104600,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減肥黎講 跑得耐但慢好快過跑得短但快</blockquote><br />\n我最近心肺都好似差左 跑十分鐘，心跳好似跌出黎咁<br />\n跟住扮跑（即係足球開死球慢慢回防果種）<br />\n但乳酸仲湧晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92702962f28a70de417380dbe807945f28e4cdf0","tid":104600,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減肥黎講 跑得耐但慢好快過跑得短但快</blockquote><br />\n我都個跑45 分鐘好<br />\n但耐左冇做運動<br />\n同樓主差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1732c849986abf8dd6715b215ef43dc98c3b63cf","tid":104600,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"食少d好過啦"},{"pid":"46a20ae1fc93bf4b11aa7668abaca787cec3d38f","tid":104600,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"主要原因都係165<br />\n面對現實啦減乜撚"},{"pid":"b502d683c17baba06a64f9c37a51289a59b8eadf","tid":104600,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"主要原因都係165<br />\n面對現實啦減乜撚"},{"pid":"2090d1f2ad404d196f7cfe50e2e6d9976741085f","tid":104600,"uid":72277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要原因都係165<br />\n面對現實啦減乜撚</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n跑少少啊吱啊咗<br />\n唔辛苦跑黎托呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb0d98dad7882921a25fa0ec8c7b30db606721","tid":104600,"uid":53163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"跑步最辛苦係頭15分鐘, 會覺得呢段時間過得好慢好辛苦<br />\n過左呢15分鐘辛苦感覺就會回落<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47467a1d404181bce5b71d89d0ad26cb33b510b0","tid":104600,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"慢跑就得，唔洗快，但都要feel到心跳keep住快先減到<br />\n好似心跳要到某個水平先開始會減肥，你自己search下"},{"pid":"29bcd04989d80052b50c2473900232ebe98cb01c","tid":104600,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"其實你唔肥<br />\n我170,但係70+kg<br />\n我跑步都唔係好得，練左好耐，但係跑一個鐘就頂唔順，跑步個人覺得主要係要操控住呼吸節奏<br />\n如果要減得快，跳繩+跑步減得好快，懶可以做7 mins"},{"pid":"e1bd4ac7d078a06b1289a6db69b09346d799b7e4","tid":104600,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"游水/踩車"},{"pid":"bf5165e1c845d73638a4c3f6b7b002ffa804fdff","tid":104600,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"做多少少腳部負重先(squat/deadlift/lunge)<br />\n做耐咗玩跑步冇咁快收皮 容易啲撐到頭10幾分鐘"},{"pid":"dbb42dccea77ece493abfd4fd89b4ad5f71f8638","tid":104600,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主要原因都係165<br />\n面對現實啦減乜撚</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n跑少少啊吱啊咗<br />\n唔辛苦跑黎托呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夏榮都高過樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd2cf67d3804c3ab56f5102ae31a02b95fba793","tid":104600,"uid":54957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"去啲多女嘅地方，望住佢哋個美尻跑"},{"pid":"38d47bb1e2b49db691eb614ee02975826cb54d1d","tid":104600,"uid":72460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"之前有無跑開？如果無跑開可能真係得10分鐘貨仔，但唔緊要，可以慢慢加上去，GoDone跑步post有資料可以睇睇，有教點樣循序漸進"},{"pid":"a9d90178a2c5c9a88acdd12b5e0798fa5fa2b294","tid":104600,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去啲多女嘅地方，望住佢哋個美尻跑</blockquote><br />\n呢個真。 唔跑開既人 隻腳係好快變得好重咁。<br />\n睇靚女係個好方法"},{"pid":"8e1590b01dc5f3fb2d8f7800e52fa3e466db7752","tid":104600,"uid":17123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:07:30.000Z","msg":"可以試吓調吓個頻率<br />\n我扁平足同氣管窄 一長跑就pk<br />\n試吓跑兩個圈慢嘅 然後爆一個圈 <br />\n不斷循環"},{"pid":"2a684690eaed54f0322af003fd96ebfc8ddb00be","tid":104600,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下基本資料先   <br />\n<br />\n27歲   165高   65kg  <br />\n手腳有肉但唔&quot;泡&quot;   主要有胃腩+肚腩<br />\n<br />\n而家做緊跑步帶氧燒脂  +   做機增肌  <br />\n跑步速度中上   但經常跑十分鐘已經想放棄    (身已暖但未出汗)   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呼吸還可以    但對腳愈黎愈重   均速再跑都難   減速跑會仲辛苦<br />\n加速....唔好玩啦   會仆街  <br />\n咁既情況係咪肌肉耐力唔夠?  <br />\n<br />\n求指點</blockquote><br />\n1. 唔知你嘅所謂中上嘅速度幾多。但為燒脂而跑步，根使快，主要係時間。唔少人係用急步行嘅燒脂，效果都好好。不如你試下先。每次45～60分鐘。試完如果覺得太輕鬆，下次加快少少，總之一定要做夠時間。有時間就練下大腿小腿肌肉。習慣咗就慢慢到。<br />\n<br />\n另外好奇一問<br />\n急步行燒脂，五分鐘都已經開始流汗，你跑中上速度十分鐘都唔流汗？好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}